jew.description: Fun fact: 100% of the Cards Against Humanity writers are Jewish. Can you believe it? A Jewish comedy writer! Anything is possible in 2017.
jew.name: Jew Pack

cats.description: AT TONIGHT'S PERFORMANCE OF: The Cards Against Humanity Theatre Pack THE ROLE OF: 30 relatable cards about theatre WILL BE PLAYED BY: 30 cards about the musical CATS. We apologize for the inconvenience. Please accept this $5 refund.
cats.name: Cats Pack

00s.description: Dude, where’s my car? The 2000s Nostalgia Pack comes with 30 new cards capitalizing on the surge of dopamine that floods your brain when you think about your childhood. Chunky highlights. Butterfly clips. Bootcut jeans. Bush did 9/11. You’re such a Miranda!
00s.name: 2000s Nostalgia Pack

save.description: Remember that time when we all thought the Trump presidency was going to be an unmitigated disaster? And then Cards Against Humanity saved America? Well, we still have the cards from that. Contains 30 cards previously released as part of our 2017 Cards Against Humanity Saves America campaign. Whoops, Donald Trump is still the president. Oh god.
save.name: Cards Against Humanity Saves America Pack

reject3.description: 25 cards (23 white, 2 black) that were previously withheld from being released for one reason or another. Each co-creator picked three cards that were rejected from print.
reject3.name: Reject Pack 3

Ass.description: Back it up. Now bring it down. Lower. Down to the floor. Now wiggle it all around. Now get out your wallet and buy the all-new Ass Pack! 30 new cards regarding butts. Includes cards by visionary ass connoisseur Sir Mix-A-Lot. Round. Juicy. Spank it!
Ass.name: Ass Pack

blackbox.description: Released as part of the Blackbox Press Kit.
blackbox.name: Blackbox Press Kit

theatre.description: As the Bard once said, “All the world’s a stage, and all the men and women merely members of our target demographic.” Hark! It’s the Theatre Pack, 30 cards about those things that are like movies but they happen right in front of you. We’d like to thank our parents, our amazing director, and of course, God. Lin-Manuel Miranda’s favorite pack. All profits fund a grant program for innovative theater and comedy run by the Theater Communications Group.
theatre.name: Theatre Pack

BF2019AI.description: 30 cards actually written by a machine learning algorithm trained on our brainstorming documents.
BF2019AI.name: AI pack
